data.description: Beautiful home in Lamesa on an over-sized lot! House has been well maintained and updated. It has beautiful unique flooring in the dining area and a very large kitchen with an island. The living room has a gas or wood-burning fireplace for those cold winter evenings. This property also comes with a sunroom that leads to a large laundry room. Sitting on a corner lot, this house is surrounded by nice large mature trees and has TWO separate driveways; one of them having an RV hookup! This is a house you don't want to miss out on!!
